{"tid":2409200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情下香港有咩地方你會選擇一去再去？","createTime":"2021-02-15T15:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T15:04:45.000Z","uid":206416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"501bd628d0404a520e972ad001b061fbf169b468","tid":2409200,"uid":206416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"香港疫情持續左一年有多，好多娛樂場所、運動場所都冇開...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我諗好多人同我一樣都會上網發掘更多好食好玩嘅地方，歡迎大家留低講吓你會一去再去嘅地方，無論係食嘢、玩樂等，等大家一齊發掘更多香港好靚嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長洲<br />\n大家聽落長洲呢個名一尐都唔陌生，假期得一個字，就係迫。大家唔係因為疫情，大家會唔會特登走入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能一年先去一次，但係依家變相因為疫情，幾乎一年去4-5次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過唔同嘅街邊小食，又多選擇，最鍾意日本婆婆手卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又可以踩單車，一舉兩得。你可以話人多，係就係人多，不過都係嗰句，根據非正式統計，香港人就係咁鍾意迫架啦，你吹咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bX99tAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbX99tAM.jpg&h=35f087d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbe8389eaf5f152e9d4d7f65323e1b57cceb72dc","tid":2409200,"uid":78188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:02:59.000Z","msg":"返公司⋯⋯"},{"pid":"20383c70cbb1e93880990ab1a1a1acc514321336","tid":2409200,"uid":137038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"長洲應該係去一次就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}